Phase 10 Tasks 1-2: Window Resize and Resize Debouncer

Files changed:
  - src/terminal/mod.rs: Terminal::resize() and ResizeDebouncer

Implementation:
  - Terminal::resize(): creates TermSize, delegates to alacritty_terminal Term::resize() for content reflow
  - ResizeDebouncer: #[derive(Default)] struct coalescing rapid resize events
  - ResizeDebouncer::new(): returns default (no pending)
  - ResizeDebouncer::request(): stores latest (cols, rows) overwriting any previous
  - ResizeDebouncer::pending(): returns Option<(usize, usize)>
  - ResizeDebouncer::clear(): sets pending to None

Tests (6 new, 289 total):
  - resize_changes_columns: 80→120 columns
  - resize_changes_rows: 24→40 rows
  - resize_preserves_content: "Hello" survives resize
  - debouncer_no_pending_initially: starts as None
  - debouncer_stores_latest_request: second request overwrites first
  - debouncer_clear_removes_pending: clear sets to None

Quality gates: 289 tests pass, clippy clean, fmt clean
